{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The world has fallen into darkness, and only a knight of light can save it. Along the way, he finds allies with the same goal and spends coins to get health, weapons, and shields to keep fighting and defeat his enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306460/extras/preview.gif?t=1730647456\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Defeat all enemies in a room to unlock the next one. Some rooms have multiple doors to choose from.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Engage in elemental battles: Fire vs Water, Cloud vs Storm, Life vs Death</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find allies to join your battles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Upgrade your characters and unlock new weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock a variety of characters - both good and evil characters are available to unlock.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Select a difficulty level for additional content, including new enemies, bosses, characters, and weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your progress is saved - you'll never lose your weapons or upgrades. You can reset or redo any run with any character.</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306460/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730647456","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306460/page.bg.jpg?t=1730647456","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306460/91070ec43ff8f71383c885c4b3d184081ec0533e/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1730647456","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306460/91070ec43ff8f71383c885c4b3d184081ec0533e/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1730647456","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"St